      "acceptanceCriteria": "Verified CFD solver with documented V&V history, version-controlled source, and traceable test suite for hemolysis sub-models.",
      "rationale": "Commercial solver (ANSYS Fluent 2022R2) is version-controlled and has documented regression tests for flow solvers, but the user-defined hemolysis scalar transport subroutine lacks formal unit testing and code review records. SQA achieved level 2 of 4 required."
