      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation experiments conducted on the same FDA generic pump geometry under flow conditions spanning the VAD operating envelope; blood analog fluid properties within 5% of clinical values.",
      "rationale": "Validation used the FDA generic pump, not the specific VAD device geometry. Operating conditions partially overlap with VAD envelope but do not cover high-speed low-flow corner cases critical for VAD patients. Achieved level 2 of 4 required."
    },
    {
