      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative mapping between experimental boundary conditions and simulation inputs demonstrated; any discrepancies bounded and their impact on QoI assessed.",
      "rationale": "No formal equivalency analysis performed between experimental and simulation input parameters. Inlet turbulence intensity, wall roughness, and fluid temperature were not matched. Impact of these discrepancies on hemolysis index not quantified. Achieved level 1 of 4 required."
